dct_description_sm: Cartographic Details: Scale approximately 1:57,000. Facsimile: location of original and date of reproduction unknown. Scale of original [1:45,258], engraved by William Bracher and printed by F. Bourquin, Philadelphia, hand colored by C. Kaufmann and mounted by Smith & Stroup. Summary: Shows land ownership.
